msgid ""
"PayPal buttons (e.g. Pay Later, Venmo, SEPA, iDEAL, Mercado Pago, "
"Bancontact, etc.) are shown automatically based on factors such as the "
"buyer’s country and their device type. By default, all buttons are enabled. "
"To disable individual payment buttons, use the \"Disable Specific Payment "
"Buttons\" setting available in each page section below.<br><br>For Express "
"Checkout, it will follow the configuration from the Checkout Page.<br>For "
"Mini Cart, this setting will follow the configuration from the Product Page."
msgstr ""
"Butang PayPal (contohnya Pay Later, Venmo, SEPA, iDEAL, Mercado Pago, "
"Bancontact, dan lain-lain) akan ditunjukkan secara automatik berdasarkan "
"faktor seperti negara pembeli dan jenis peranti mereka. Secara lalai, semua "
"butang diaktifkan. Untuk menyahaktifkan butang pembayaran tertentu, gunakan "
"tetapan \"Disable Specific Payment Buttons\" yang tersedia di setiap "
"bahagian halaman di bawah.<br><br>Untuk Express Checkout, ia akan mengikuti "
"konfigurasi dari Halaman Checkout.<br>Untuk Mini Cart, tetapan ini akan "
"mengikuti konfigurasi dari Halaman Produk."

