#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:447
msgid ""
"Choose where the PayPal buttons should appear on the cart page, either above "
"or below the \"Proceed to Checkout\" button. This applies only to classic "
"cart templates, not the new Cart Blocks layout."
msgstr ""
"Pilih di mana butang PayPal harus muncul di halaman troli, sama ada di atas "
"atau di bawah butang \"Proceed to Checkout\". Ini hanya terpakai untuk "
"templat troli klasik, bukan susun atur Cart Blocks yang baru."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:451
