"Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Malta, Netherlands, Norway, "
"Poland, Portugal, Romania, Singapore, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, "
"United States, United Kingdom<br><br>"
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran Kad Kredit/Debit Lanjutan tidak diaktifkan dalam akaun PayPal "
"anda. <br><br><strong>Negara yang Disokong:</strong><br>Australia, Austria, "
"Belgium, Bulgaria, Kanada, China, Cyprus, Republik Czech, Denmark, Estonia, "
"Finland, Perancis, Jerman, Greece, Hong Kong, Hungary, Ireland, Itali, "
"Jepun, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Malta, Belanda, Norway, "
"Poland, Portugal, Romania, Singapura, Slovakia, Slovenia, Sepanyol, Sweden, "
"Amerika Syarikat, United Kingdom<br><br>"

